assessment_details.task_description:
The aim of this assessment task is to increase the students's knowledge across the breadth of the Course content from week 1 through week 13 AND as applied to a continuing Performance Management case study from week 8 through week 13. This is achieved by a combination of:

pre-reading the specified chapter of the text (Aguines, 2014) and/or specified required readings (BlackBoard);

completion of the Learning unit pro forma for that week;

pre-reading of the Case Study; and

making notes in the Case Discussion pro forma for that case study (group and/or individual, weeks 8 - 13).
